Koga Shuko and the newcomers arrive at the CF with guns firing.
Koga Shuko: Hello Hot Rod. I know you were expecting an attack from Hell 
Beast's forces, but unfortunately he is a bit slow to act. We are an 
organized crime group of Predacons not allied with Hell Beast and no we won't 
be as easy as his warriors.
He takes a direct shot at Hot Rod.

Ares flies out in ground assualt mode with many guns and fires at the 
Maximals.
Unitron, Hades, Anubis, and Serpentor do the same.
